{"blogid": "126742977", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "107", "writerCollect": "140", "writerComment": "2", "writerFan": "11", "writerGrade": "4级", "writerIntegral": "1092", "writerName": "脚踏实地的大梦想家", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_126742977.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "23320", "writerRankWeekly": "37442", "writerThumb": "49", "writerVisitNum": "66903", "blog_read_count": "9", "blog_time": "于 2022-09-07 12:25:30 发布", "blog_title": "【python基础】P6 基础循环", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<p>python中最常用的循环语句是for</p>\n<h1><a id=\"_2\"></a>例：循环打印出列表中所有的值</h1>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\">car <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"BMW\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"VOLVO\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"BENZ\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"RR\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> car<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b1c54ff68efd464aa38a0b4fd0e5961b.png\"/><br/> 在循环语句for中，i的第一次被赋值为car[0]，然后通过print打印出；第二次为car[1]，然后通过print打印出…直到car中所有的元素被访问且打印。</p>\n<p>python循环中一定要注意缩进，python中的缩进就像C语言中的{}。</p>\n<hr/>\n<h1><a id=\"range_15\"></a>range()，通过范围生成数字</h1>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">range</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c8b9eef9ffe9447f83f03f1b74985299.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>另外一种方法依次打印出列表car中所有的元素：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\">car <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'BMW'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'VOLVO'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'BENZ'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'RR'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">range</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>car<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>car<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\eaa2d16647814887a393eec22cbc4dad.png\"/><br/> 其中通过 <strong>len(car)</strong> 获取列表 car 中元素的个数，值为4；<br/> 再通过 <strong>range(len(car))</strong> 建立一个范围取值，range(4) 即为 0-3。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>当然，range(x,y) 可以通过起始值x和终止值+1的y来规定其取值范围：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">range</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\403f601317a6481597fd9e9fcf040fd1.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>如果用list再对range进行包裹，则可以形成一个数字列表</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\">x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">range</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\627f26cf020243738d0e577f66839676.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>对range的进一步规定，可以规定其步长</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\">x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">range</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\2689222b351b478aa5b64e7a10dda4e7.png\"/><br/> 在上述code中，range(x,y,z)，其中x为起始，y为终止-1，z为步长。<br/> 所谓步长，就是每一步的长度，也就是x=1的下一个元素为x+z。</p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Python", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 1, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-09-07 12:25:30", "summary": "中最常用的循环语句是例：循环打印出列表中所有的值在这里插入图片描述在循环语句中，的第一次被赋值为，然后通过打印出；第二次为，然后通过打印出直到中所有的元素被访问且打印。循环中一定要注意缩进，中的缩进就"}